Does the maximum LOS distance change?
Yes. Increasing the gateway height extends the maximum Line-of-Sight distance from approximately 21.1 km to 23.2 km.

Does this noticeably improve link feasibility?
From a purely mathematical perspective using the log-distance path loss model, the improvement is relatively small. However, from a practical deployment point of view, the improvement is significant.

